Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.60,0:01:56.59,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Good afternoon, Renji-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.18,0:02:01.10,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Good afternoon. You took your time today.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.10,0:02:03.85,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I finished writing the novel.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.60,0:02:07.86,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I wrote the last part myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.86,0:02:10.36,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,I-I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.75,0:02:12.11,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.62,0:02:14.11,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations on completing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.11,0:02:16.28,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.28,0:02:20.01,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,But it's not done yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.01,0:02:23.29,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,After you finish reading it, if there isn't a problem, then it's done.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.78,0:02:27.79,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,This is something the two of us wrote together.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.79,0:02:30.20,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Which ending did you choose?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.37,0:02:36.45,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Did you end it with the girl entering the paintings, or the boy coming out of the paintings?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.04,0:02:39.53,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't decided on the ending yet, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.53,0:02:42.31,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,About that... you'll know when you read it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.31,0:02:43.14,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.27,0:02:45.27,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Please wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.27,0:02:48.90,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Please read it after I've gone home.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.33,0:02:50.77,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,It's embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.86,0:02:54.21,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I should express my gratitude to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.21,0:02:55.19,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Gratitude?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.19,0:03:01.05,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't have finished writing the novel by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.05,0:03:03.20,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,This is all thanks to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.20,0:03:05.64,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.64,0:03:08.37,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,You had the ability to write it to begin with.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.37,0:03:14.09,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,No. I don't think I could've done anything without you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.52,0:03:20.13,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,You created the chance for me to fulfill my only dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.64,0:03:24.90,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, with this, I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.71,0:03:29.62,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Please let me express my gratitude to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.62,0:03:32.53,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I want to express my gratitude to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.53,0:03:34.11,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Chihiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.11,0:03:37.28,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,If there's anything I can do, please tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.77,0:03:40.61,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Then... will you go on a date with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.61,0:03:43.37,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,A... date?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.80,0:03:44.69,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.24,0:03:48.31,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Going on a date is something lovers do.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.31,0:03:50.87,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Can't we be lovers?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.32,0:03:57.38,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,As I thought. I won't do after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.38,0:04:00.43,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,That's not... It's not like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.94,0:04:04.93,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. Let's be lovers.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.93,0:04:07.31,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,But only for one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.31,0:04:08.89,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Only for one day?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.89,0:04:14.19,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. You and I will be lovers only for tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.19,0:04:16.41,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,So let's have a date.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.41,0:04:17.82,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Only for tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.25,0:04:20.40,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,It's called a trial period.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.40,0:04:22.72,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Then how about starting the day after tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.72,0:04:24.82,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Let me think about it tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.54,0:04:29.91,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Can you read the novel another time?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.97,0:04:34.24,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Please read it after our date tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.09,0:04:44.64,Main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,The two of you are really similar.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.10,0:04:47.64,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Who am I similar to?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.64,0:04:50.39,Main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder. I've already forgotten about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.39,0:04:53.42,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,The person you're waiting for?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.42,0:04:55.37,Main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,I forgot about her too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.03,0:04:56.95,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Erm...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.95,0:04:57.90,Main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.90,0:05:01.78,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,What does it feel like to fall in love with someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.16,0:05:05.12,Main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see. You feel like there's no helping it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.12,0:05:06.45,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,There's no helping...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.45,0:05:09.00,Main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,When you finally notice, it's already too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.00,0:05:12.54,Main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,It's too late no matter how you feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.54,0:05:16.29,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, it might be too late for me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.73,0:05:17.67,Main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.67,0:05:22.28,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Erm, thank you for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.28,0:05:24.30,Main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter? You're so formal.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.30,0:05:26.21,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I just felt like saying it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.21,0:05:31.31,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,If I don't say it when I want to, I'll forget about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.07,0:05:34.40,Main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.40,0:05:37.06,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,You said the same thing as Renji-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.21,0:05:40.11,Main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,We're similar too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.10,0:05:42.80,Main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Give this to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.80,0:05:44.11,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.11,0:05:46.36,Main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Just a little custom.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.62,0:05:52.37,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.27,0:05:57.71,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,M-Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.20,0:05:59.81,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.81,0:06:01.66,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing... those clothes...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.66,0:06:05.26,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Since it's a date, I dressed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.26,0:06:10.05,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-chan bought it for me, even though I didn't try it on before.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.52,0:06:12.81,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,It's great. It's really cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.25,0:06:15.06,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.32,0:06:19.88,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have a plan in mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.88,0:06:23.49,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,I thought about seeing a movie first.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.49,0:06:24.58,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.58,0:06:25.86,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,That sounds good.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.30,0:06:27.92,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of movie should we see?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.92,0:06:30.49,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,I guess... at a time like this, a love story would be best...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.49,0:06:32.79,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,As long as it's not a sad one.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.79,0:06:34.48,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Not a sad one?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.48,0:06:37.83,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I might cry real hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.33,0:06:40.13,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Then how about a comedy?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.13,0:06:43.13,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,That sounds good. I like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.63,0:06:52.43,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... sorry. Well, I didn't think it would have a bad ending.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.43,0:06:53.76,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,That was totally unexpected.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.28,0:07:02.73,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. I-I'm... going to... wash my face...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.13,0:07:04.33,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Do you need a tissue?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.33,0:07:05.65,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I brought some with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.52,0:07:08.19,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.19,0:07:08.99,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.99,0:07:12.48,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,It was a really good story though.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.48,0:07:15.20,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,It was interesting how the story took an unexpected turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.20,0:07:19.27,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it would be slapstick, but it turned out to have emotional development.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.27,0:07:20.50,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.91,0:07:23.29,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,And it had a bad ending.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.29,0:07:26.25,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,A happy ending would've been nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.25,0:07:28.26,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,It would've ... really been...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.64,0:07:34.76,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to wash my face.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.76,0:07:37.81,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Erm... do you need tissues?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.81,0:07:39.27,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,You're mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.55,0:07:44.48,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Where are we going next?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.48,0:07:51.60,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see. Since you don't like crowded places, a game center wouldn't work out...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.14,0:07:58.31,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Want to give it a try?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.31,0:07:59.00,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.90,0:08:05.35,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,That was a bit hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.75,0:08:11.53,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,The setup of the spring was weak, and the material was slippery.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.15,0:08:16.06,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,The rabbit next to it seemed to be easy though.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.85,0:08:21.69,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah. I'll buy you a similar one next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.69,0:08:23.14,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,I know a place that sells them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.14,0:08:25.15,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Our eyes met.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.65,0:08:28.90,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,It said I should bring it with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.94,0:08:32.53,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.31,0:08:37.33,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,You want that one, right? I'll definitely get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.73,0:08:42.23,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,This time for sure. This time for sure. This time for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.23,0:08:43.04,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.04,0:08:44.64,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.64,0:08:46.20,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Don't slip off.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.20,0:08:50.35,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Keep going... Keep going... Keep going...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.35,0:08:51.30,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.60,0:08:54.16,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Finally got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.16,0:08:55.05,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.05,0:08:57.30,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.10,0:08:58.80,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Poyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.80,0:08:59.81,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Poyo?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.81,0:09:04.06,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,The one I have at home is Piyo-chan. This one is Poyo-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.06,0:09:05.64,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,I-I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.12,0:09:08.65,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Can we play that one too?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.52,0:09:14.95,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Please give me one piece.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.95,0:09:17.46,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,There are plenty of them. Let's split them half-and-half.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.46,0:09:19.40,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Just one piece is enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.40,0:09:20.16,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.79,0:09:26.00,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Renji-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.40,0:09:27.33,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.96,0:09:29.92,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Today was really fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.36,0:09:31.42,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,That's good to hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.25,0:09:34.59,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Erm, Renji-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.59,0:09:35.38,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.73,0:09:38.51,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Can we... hold hands?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.64,0:09:40.42,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.51,0:09:43.58,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.58,0:09:44.98,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,We're lovers, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.98,0:09:46.37,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.03,0:09:52.12,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Somehow I always feel at ease when I'm with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.90,0:09:54.69,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.69,0:09:56.92,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go to the beach if that's okay with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.92,0:09:57.99,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,The beach?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.99,0:10:00.78,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,It seems lovers go to the beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.16,0:10:02.19,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.19,0:10:04.95,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. That's what the books say.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.60,0:10:13.49,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,What do lovers do after they come here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.01,0:10:18.61,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,It wouldn't be bad just to remain like this, without doing anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.61,0:10:19.90,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.56,0:10:24.55,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,We came here before too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.55,0:10:25.43,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.43,0:10:28.68,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,A lot of things happened, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.68,0:10:29.94,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.94,0:10:35.57,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,A lot of things happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.57,0:10:39.12,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I know about them because I've read my diary over and over again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.12,0:10:41.44,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't remember them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.42,0:10:45.58,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure by tomorrow I'll also forget about today's...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.54,0:10:49.29,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be nice if tomorrow never came.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.29,0:10:52.09,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't say something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.09,0:10:55.80,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Couldn't tomorrow possibly be a better day than today?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.82,0:11:00.05,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.05,0:11:03.27,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I totally forgot about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.27,0:11:07.06,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Himura-san told me to give this to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.06,0:11:11.48,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently, it's a duplicate key to the school rooftop.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.48,0:11:13.31,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Huh, why?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.31,0:11:18.53,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,The view of the streets from the rooftop in the evening is supposed to be really beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.53,0:11:22.82,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,That's not what I meant. Why did Himura-san have this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.82,0:11:25.33,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder why.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.33,0:11:27.58,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,He's a really mysterious person.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.23,0:11:34.28,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently, it's a custom in that school to pass down this key from one person to another.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.70,0:11:37.17,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Eh. Let's go and try it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.17,0:11:38.30,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.60,0:11:46.03,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.03,0:11:48.38,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,I should thank Himura-san after this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.38,0:11:49.93,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.43,0:11:51.52,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing, amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.98,0:11:54.56,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get too close to the edge.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.56,0:11:56.31,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.23,0:12:01.08,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,It's really amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.08,0:12:02.40,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.95,0:12:03.95,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Chihiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.95,0:12:04.82,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.23,0:12:06.32,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.60,0:12:13.79,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,I'll also love you tomorrow and the day after. I'll always love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.63,0:12:18.49,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Saying something like that doesn't suit me, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.49,0:12:20.92,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,I yearned to say it though.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.41,0:12:23.55,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.77,0:12:26.78,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Can we kiss?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.78,0:12:29.61,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Kissing is something lovers do.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.61,0:12:31.70,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,I'm your lover.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.70,0:12:35.86,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, you should just kiss me without saying anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.86,0:12:36.81,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.36,0:12:38.31,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.21,0:12:44.57,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Our teeth knocked against each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.97,0:12:47.87,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Then... let's try it one more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.25,0:12:55.71,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry. I got a little carried away.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.50,0:12:59.36,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.45,0:13:04.16,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I've finally come all the way here today.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.16,0:13:08.05,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want you to treat me like I'm far away.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.05,0:13:09.83,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Chihiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.83,0:13:14.33,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Please make us into a real pair of lovers.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.56,0:13:23.58,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Why me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.58,0:13:25.11,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder why.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.11,0:13:27.65,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,How about you? Why me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.65,0:13:30.39,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder why. Just that...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.39,0:13:31.03,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Just that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.03,0:13:34.72,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I love you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.12,0:13:37.04,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Chihiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.56,0:13:41.52,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.52,0:13:42.73,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.73,0:13:43.62,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.62,0:13:45.37,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.37,0:13:46.86,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.86,0:13:48.05,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Renji-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.05,0:13:48.72,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.72,0:13:49.47,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Kiss.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.47,0:13:51.51,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.42,0:13:53.58,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.77,0:14:02.17,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Geez.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.02,0:14:05.28,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Is it about today?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.28,0:14:08.26,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, about just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.26,0:14:09.53,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,What have you written?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.53,0:14:12.03,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I won't tell anyone no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.03,0:14:14.64,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me what you can then.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.64,0:14:17.08,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, our teeth knocked against each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.22,0:14:21.47,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,You were right. You can't say anything beyond that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.47,0:14:22.88,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.27,0:14:29.71,MainT,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Ten o'clock in the evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.71,0:14:35.52,MainT,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,That means the memory of our meeting at the station at nine this morning will disappear soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.01,0:14:45.31,MainT,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,From now on, an hour of Chihiro's memories about what happened today will disappear as each hour passes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.84,0:14:56.45,MainT,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,They will all disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.64,0:15:00.88,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Renji-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.45,0:15:04.08,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing. It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.58,0:15:07.59,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Everything is fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.09,0:15:15.70,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Today has passed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.70,0:15:16.50,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.50,0:15:18.72,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Your trial period has passed, hasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.06,0:15:22.50,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,You brought it with you, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.50,0:15:26.64,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, please read it. Then it will be completed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.36,0:15:28.61,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Chihiro?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.61,0:15:32.31,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I'm embarrassed after all for you to read it in front of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.31,0:15:36.52,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I'll read this on the rooftop.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.52,0:15:41.41,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I want to reread all the things that have happened from when we met up until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.77,0:15:46.02,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Please tell me after you've finished reading it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.02,0:15:47.02,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.02,0:15:48.25,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,See you later then.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.25,0:15:48.92,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.94,0:15:50.94,Notes Box,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}A
Dialogue: 1,0:15:48.94,0:15:50.94,Notes,TL Note,0000,0000,0000,,The furigana next to it says "Kanjou", which means "Feelings."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.92,0:15:53.17,MainT,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,"The girl is the only one in the world."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.95,0:15:55.95,Notes Box,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}A
Dialogue: 1,0:15:50.95,0:15:55.95,Notes,TL Note,0000,0000,0000,,Reference Note: Most of the lines below can be found in the opening animation.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.60,0:15:55.93,MainT,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,"That made her the God of this world."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.56,0:15:58.85,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,"Something mysterious happened."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.85,0:16:01.30,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,"The two in those paintings had moved."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.11,0:16:05.60,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,"The god looked inside the paintings."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.56,0:16:10.25,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,"The two in the pictures seemed to be having fun, smiling at each other."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.25,0:16:12.47,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,"But the paintings were blurred."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.47,0:16:14.57,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,"The world itself appeared blurred."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.18,0:16:18.53,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,"Why, the girl thought."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.59,0:16:22.63,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,"A strange feeling developed in her mind."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.63,0:16:26.09,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,"She could not describe what it was."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.96,0:16:31.23,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,"She wondered why the paintings became blurred, even though she painted them so clearly."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.10,0:16:34.52,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,"The two in the paintings were smiling at each other."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.13,0:16:36.96,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,"That was what she felt."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.08,0:16:40.09,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,"She repainted them."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.09,0:16:42.50,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,"She repainted them over and over."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.50,0:16:45.69,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,"But the results were exactly the same."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.29,0:16:48.60,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,"She was at a loss."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.60,0:16:51.40,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,"She began to be unsure of everything."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.47,0:16:54.69,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,"The girl is the only one in the world."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.69,0:16:57.03,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,"That made her the God of this world."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.56,0:17:01.85,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,"So she thought she should make her world much cleaner."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.20,0:17:05.70,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,"She burned all pictures."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.58,0:17:09.08,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,"She set fire to the mansion and the old castle."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.08,0:17:13.84,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,"Along with the structures, she burned all her memories."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.29,0:17:21.84,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,"Lastly, the God threw the trash, the only trash left in the world, out from the cliff."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.08,0:17:35.23,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Renji-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.23,0:17:38.11,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,I finished reading the novel.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.59,0:17:39.83,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,How was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.83,0:17:42.63,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm, I was a bit surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.63,0:17:44.21,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,It's a sad ending.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.58,0:17:46.99,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.99,0:17:51.46,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,For the girl, it's the happiest ending.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.50,0:17:57.04,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,The girl shouldn't have contact with other people after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.04,0:17:59.44,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Because she has found out what loneliness is.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.44,0:18:00.72,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Chihiro...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.72,0:18:03.97,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,That girl is us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.18,0:18:07.81,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Renji-kun, let's break up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.75,0:18:10.81,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.81,0:18:14.31,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you're obstinate about it, I won't give way about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.67,0:18:15.31,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.68,0:18:16.86,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.36,0:18:18.38,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.38,0:18:21.36,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Did I tell you the story of the sheep?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.46,0:18:27.68,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,The story about the sheep tied by a chain, that died after eating up all the grass.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.68,0:18:28.20,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.62,0:18:33.08,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I'm tied by a chain that's twelve years long.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.08,0:18:37.99,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how much time goes by, I can't get to the outside world from there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.99,0:18:40.71,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,The farthest my hand can reach is thirteen hours from there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.59,0:18:46.40,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,The story I wrote was about my dream inside those twelve years.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.06,0:18:51.59,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,That's why after I finished writing the story, everything of mine is done.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.64,0:18:54.62,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I decided at the very beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.12,0:18:59.61,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I'd disappear from your sight after I finished writing this novel.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.51,0:19:09.37,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I'd disappear quietly without leaving behind any memories, like a mermaid princess turning into a bubble.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.37,0:19:15.21,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm weak. I became like Cinderella instead of a mermaid princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.21,0:19:20.84,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,That's all right. It's ridiculous to call me a prince, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.84,0:19:23.34,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,You're wrong, Renji-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.51,0:19:26.63,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I was happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.63,0:19:29.05,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I was really, really happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.05,0:19:31.57,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.57,0:19:38.81,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,But, since I'm like this, I don't want you to disappear from my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.56,0:19:43.07,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I want to break up while I can still say, "I love you."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.51,0:19:44.83,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.83,0:19:47.07,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,That logic doesn't make sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.07,0:19:51.83,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,You let me write the novel that I abandoned a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.18,0:19:56.11,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,You let me wear a uniform and go to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.11,0:20:01.35,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,You brought me out of the station where I was marooned.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.86,0:20:07.16,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Before then, I had been doing nothing but looking up at the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.72,0:20:10.62,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I always felt like crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.19,0:20:15.85,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I always looked up at the sky because I felt like my tears were going to start.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.82,0:20:21.37,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,You hugged someone like me tightly.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.98,0:20:26.45,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,You suffered and cried for my sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.02,0:20:31.06,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I want you to be happy too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.71,0:20:33.28,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want you to be unhappy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.28,0:20:34.29,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Chihiro...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.64,0:20:41.14,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,If you stay with me, I believe you'll keep suffering from painful memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.66,0:20:44.17,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.36,0:20:47.66,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not disappearing because I hate you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.21,0:20:52.40,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Even I have a way to prevent you from being unhappy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.10,0:20:57.77,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I shouldn't be able to do anything, I've found a way.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.77,0:20:58.77,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.77,0:21:00.52,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Please praise me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.52,0:21:02.65,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.65,0:21:06.78,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,How can I praise you for something stupid like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.78,0:21:08.32,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Please smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.32,0:21:09.40,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.78,0:21:13.66,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Let's part with your usual smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.66,0:21:14.91,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.77,0:21:17.70,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.16,0:21:21.42,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Farewell.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.84,0:21:32.43,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Chihiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.47,0:21:34.39,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.77,0:21:41.31,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,This is me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.27,0:21:45.81,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,The diary from the day I met you until today.
